channel.title: Download from Sendspace (Instant download, No membership required)
channel.description:
1.Copy The sendspace link Example: http://www.sendspace.com/file/tablfn , (Grand Theft Auto San andreas) if you're wondering
2.Go to www.google.com and click on language tools[URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img295.imageshack.us/img295/6127/languageez4.png[/img][/URL]
3.Copy and paste link in [b]"Translate a webpage"[/b] And Select [b]"English to spanish"[/b] And click [b]"Translate"[/b] . [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img225.imageshack.us/img225/5739/untitledpv4.png[/img][/URL]
4.Wait for the page to load.. and click on the link next to "Acoplamiento de la transferencia directa:<insert filename here> and the download should begin [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img216.imageshack.us/img216/6780/translatevc0.png[/img][/URL]
Note:This Tutorial was made and created by me Feel Free To Post on other fourms just as long as you give credit to me . As you can see i have 1337 uB3R H4x0r paint skills That i'm sure you're all jelous of.
